 - Rows now have a selectable property and will be
   styled accordingly

* Inspector:
 - Add an easy way to change the font
 - Show widget state and other misc. info

* Wayland:
 - Fix repaint artifacts
 - Update xdg-shell

* Windows:
 - Fix icon theme loading

